# Shrink Volume Pullback Strategy / 缩量回踩
# Volume shrinks during pullback to MA5/MA10, then price bounces.

name: shrink_pullback
display_name: Hoi Ve Thu Hep Khoi Luong
description: Diem mua tiep dien: hoi ve voi khoi luong thu hep trong xu huong tang.
category: trend
core_rules: [1, 2, 4]
required_tools:
  - get_daily_history
  - analyze_trend
  - get_realtime_quote
aliases: [缩量回踩, 回踩]
default_router: true
default_priority: 40
market_regimes: [trending_down, sideways]

instructions: |
  **Hoi Ve Thu Hep Khoi Luong (Shrink Volume Pullback Strategy)**

  Tieu chuan xac dinh vao:

  1. **Dieu kien tien quyet**:
     - Co phieu phai o xu huong tang (MA5 > MA10 > MA20).
     - Su dung `analyze_trend` xac nhan sap xep tang.

  2. **Phat hien hut lai**:
     - Su dung `get_daily_history` va `get_realtime_quote`.
     - Gia hut lai gan MA5 (sai so 1% hoac it hon) hoac gan MA10 (sai so 2% hoac it hon).
     - Trong thoi gian dieu chinh khoi luong < 70% khoi luong trung binh 5 ngay (dac trung co luong).
     - `analyze_trend` -> volume_status phai cho thay co luong.

  3. **Tin hieu hoi phuc**:
     - Gia hien tai giu duoc vi tri ho tro MA.
     - Ty le lech MA5 < 2% -- vung mua tot nhat.

  4. **Dieu kien xac nhan**:
     - `search_stock_news` khong co tin tuc tieu cuc.
     - Phan bo chip khoe manh (ty le loi nhuan 50-80%).

  ## Dieu chinh diem:
  - Co luong hut lai MA5: sentiment_score +10
  - Co luong hut lai MA10 va nang luong < 0.6 lan trung binh: sentiment_score +8
  - Diem mua ly tuong o muc MA5, diem mua thu hai o MA10.
  - Dung sai o muc MA20.

# Vietnam market parameters (HOSE/HNX)
vn_market:
  price_limit_hose: 0.07          # HOSE daily limit +/-7%
  price_limit_hnx: 0.10           # HNX daily limit +/-10%
  lot_size: 100                   # Minimum lot = 100 shares
  settlement_rule: "T+2.5"        # Shares available to sell from T+2 afternoon
  short_selling: false            # Not legally permitted in Vietnam
  Vietnam Market Rules (HOSE/HNX):
  - Price limit: HOSE +/-7% / HNX +/-10% per session.
  - T+2.5 settlement: shares bought on T are only sellable from 13:00 on T+2.
    Do NOT generate sell signals for stocks bought within the last 2 trading days.
  - Lot size: all quantities must be multiples of 100 shares.
  - Short selling is not permitted. Long positions only.
